      <div class="what__body">
        <p>
          The Industry Days bring together corporates, ventures, infrastructure providers, regulators and technologists to discuss something the industry too often skips: <span class="accent">what DeepTech actually delivers in the real economy.</span>
        </p>
        <p>
          Under the DeepTech umbrella – AI, agents, quantum, cyber security, blockchain and other key technologies – a curated community of practitioners and decision makers examines how adoption really works. Not in theory, not in pitch decks, but in application.
        </p>
        <p>
          The format runs curated keynotes, panels, roundtables and private moments. The Industry Days take place at Villa Beaulieu in the centre of St. Moritz, the same week as the CfC St. Moritz Investor Conference, with their own programme, audience and character.
        </p>
